  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="Aink23-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">  ituvumatu. </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="Aink23">
        <lg type="edition">
<l>          muḷḷi vēraḷaik kaḷva ṉāṭṭip</l>
<l>          pūkkuṟ ṟeytiya puṉalaṇi yūraṉ</l>
<l>          ṟēṟṟañ ceytunap puṇarntiṉit</l>
<l>          tākkaṇaṅ kāva tevaṉko laṉṉāy.</l>

        </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>          The man from the village adorned by a flood </l>
<l rend="indent2">          that reached, plucking flowers,</l>
<l rend="indent2">          chasing the crab [back] into [its] hole by the Muḷḷi roots–</l>
<l>        His making [things] clear, uniting with us [and] now</l>
<l rend="indent2">        becoming a torment that attacks [us]: </l>
<l>        What [of it], mother?</l>
        
        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
